text: Zhang Kexin (; ; born 5 June 2002) is a Chinese freestyle skier. She competed in the 2018 Winter Olympics in the women's halfpipe. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Freestyle skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Chinese female freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of China Category:Skiers from Harbin
